snippet.title: Scrabdackle - Demo Release Teaser
snippet.description:
New demo available now on Steam! Try it and wishlist at: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1578720/Scrabdackle/

Join the Discord! https://discord.gg/bUY6HP8

Scrabdackle is a game made by a solo developer (that's me!) targeting a 2023 release. It's a hand-drawn, non-linear zeldalike adventure about going exploring, with a vast, intricate overworld, tight and responsive combat, cheeky banter, and pages of lore to discover – all under a coat of playful charm. 

Music is original by jakefriend.
